 * [@aradalvand comment about recent hopes and potential solution](https://github.com/sveltejs/svelte/issues/6972#issuecomment-1371679372)
 * [@AdaptingAFM comment on slot style tag](https://github.com/sveltejs/rfcs/pull/66#issuecomment-1372325987)

