Other reactivity libraries like [SolidJS](https://www.solidjs.com/tutorial/reactivity_batch), [effector](https://effector.dev/docs/advanced-guide/computation-priority/), and [Preact Signals](https://github.com/preactjs/signals#batchfn) include utilities that let you batch updates to stores, effectively solving this problem.

